## Project Information

- **Name**: FileENIAC
- **Version**: 0.1.3
- **Description**: Local-first workspace management platform combining Git repository management, GitHub integration, and FTPS deployment orchestration through a unified dashboard.
- **Author**: Joao Aschenbrenner / ENIAC Systems
- **License**: MIT

## Core Functionality

- Local workspace lifecycle management with discovery and registry
- Git repository operations (clone, pull, push, diff)
- GitHub personal access token integration and repository discovery
- FTPS deployment orchestration with rollback and verification
- Bidirectional mirror synchronization
- Deploy history and audit logging
- Background health monitoring

