## Data Storage

All data is stored locally on the user's device. No data is transmitted to
the developer or any third-party servers except as strictly necessary for
GitHub personal access token authentication (tokens are stored locally) and FTPS operations
(data transfer between the user's device and their configured FTPS servers).

See DATA_PROCESSING.md and PRIVACY_POLICY.md for details.